column3: Successfully tested all MET sensor inputs, RF modem, IM data, and GPS (with rooftop antenna), waiting for SIM card.
Ran Bench current drain test for  7 days with version 2.01, 170530 firmware, but Patrick stopped my running average when he used my multimeter, but average was around 14mA.
Ran Bench current drain test AGAIN for 3 days with average current drain of 13.33mA.  Flash RAM data dump looked good.
Successfully tested internal GPS & Iridium antenna by doing an GPS & XMIT outside.
